name: Kalapathik  Sanskrutik Evam Bahuuddeshiya Sanstha
briefDescription: Kalapathik Sanskrutik Evam Bahuuddeshiya Sanstha  is an institution of Central India which has been working in mass awareness and social reforms through art and culture for many years. many programs such as like save water, save environment, plant trees, save trees, cleanup campaign, female feticide, daughter save, daughter teaches daughter Bachao is displayed through dramatic art and street plays.
